metadata.name: ASYM-Human Form-02
metadata.description:
Combine asymmetric organic forms to create asymmetric forms that reflect a deeper and more comprehensive perception of life's imperfections. Each asymmetric form represents how the universe's inherent imperfections enable the existence of life.

Using the following techniques, all works are created digitally: 
digital paintings and  digital collages 
By Sweeneypen

Please check my Instagram profile if you'd like to see how these works were created.
Thank you!
Happy collecting!
